title: Andy Frisella - A Collision of Limitless Minds
description: I feel that Andy is one of the greatest young entrepreneurs in America today and you're about to find out why! He is a powerhouse in the social media space and consistently delivers powerful, influential personal development and business podcasts. Not only was I impressed by his brilliant mind, but his generous and kind heart. In this interview you will see another side of Andy.
author: edwardmylett@yahoo.com (Ed Mylett)
